Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来，从那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来过这里多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，这个星球\N我思念的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那小小的女朋友，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和千濑的约定之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在那一天\N从这个地方开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个乡下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有什么乐趣可言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对未来也是茫茫然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但唯有一件事\N是我们两人自己决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个喜欢的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应她，要去她那里找她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去吧，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈有我陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心修次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都已经这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的朋友都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易诞生到这世上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时代一定会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次他们现在才要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始他们的时代、世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次那孩子的表情\N越来越坚强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N这一天我们不断地慰藉彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在疲倦之后\N宛如融合成一个身体似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不分开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偎在一起睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是恋爱的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（第一次纪念修次千濑）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC202年 萨玛之战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC73年 斯巴达克之乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC66年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前，不是有人预言\N地球什么时候会灭亡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候真的相信这种预言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还觉得\N我可能十几岁就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人哭了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想对那时候的我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她说“地球不会有事的”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这种谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就不用哭得那么伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9年 托伊头布加森林之战…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑继续缓缓的背诵着\N这个星球一个个的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如在悼念死者，为他们送终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史教科书的年表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是千濑唯一拿手的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我只是不想想起你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我只是个武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不需要恢复成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会这么痛苦，这么悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算变成孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候\N我真的希望在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！一定有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样！太可恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我期待着\N或许爱情可以救得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，现实并没有让我获得解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑还活着，她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着奋战到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给了我性爱的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我到最后一刻都要谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫我活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，陪我到这个星球\N灭亡的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易见面了\N可是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起，已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然跟你说这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你会很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这个城市\N或许感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是地球的另一端\N真的已经惨不忍赌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和地球都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市也快变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活下去的国家或是人们\N都到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个城市有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好傻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我再怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好傻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类挣扎到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要这么做才会甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上会有个超大地震\N一口气袭击整个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论再怎么努力，这个星球\N再过不久就会毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人类、大家选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我和这个国家的大人物\N很久以前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，我真的很想\N把你还有这个城市的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些我最爱的人\N全部杀光光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球毁灭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以不会感到疼痛的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以最不痛苦的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在的我办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，你却让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，我会一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你孤单一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要说什么要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么要结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我会守护这个城镇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一点点\N我也会让他们活到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，因为我是个武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会连你都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸，妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸，妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，大家对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海啸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经守护不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好难过喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让他们这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让他们早点解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们．
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是人，谁都不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸！妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了活下去而出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，为什么只有我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没留下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们留下的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确曾经存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们小小的\N滑稽又可爱的印证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，千濑，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难过吧？很痛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遵守约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于履行了我跟你的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了最后\N还是一对恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为变成这样我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很…你听，我真的很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听我说啊，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在呼唤我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在呼唤我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是千濑要我\N留在这里的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只有我一个人得救有什么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我在没有人的世界\N一个人活下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是啊，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我说我要陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我叫你活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见你的心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗通噗通的跳着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能存在你的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我全部的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明保护了你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，不能接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能抚模，也不能做爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我们可以永远在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴能够遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够这样一直跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，是千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你体内的我怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我在你的心中\N这么有份量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得见我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修\N千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，听得见\N我感觉得到你的心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你的心中这么有份量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们记住所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背负全部的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赎罪到死为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是男朋友，她是女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有昙花一现的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要互相依靠\N一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个子很小，胆子也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩也只有中下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有世界史比较强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口头禅是“对不起”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座右铭是“我想变得更坚强”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球真的已经毁灭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，已经毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球因为惧怕毁灭而发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来彷佛像是千濑的心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是这个星球与我们\N用尽最后力气所唱出的歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LOVE SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将继续相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,3000)}最终话\N「然后，我们将继续相恋」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:34.24,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:40.41,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想让这段恋情结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:45.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再见这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:50.95,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,能从这个世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:55.30,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:19.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:25.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:30.23,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:35.80,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:43.75,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
